### 로그인 → 토큰 발급
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"email":"test2@email.com","password":"1234"}

### 토큰 없이 API Key 발급 → 401 기대
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants/me/api-keys?tenantId=1
Content-Type: application/json

### 토큰 있이 API Key 발급 → 200 기대 (accessToken을 아래에 붙여넣기)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants/me/api-keys?tenantId=1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIzIiwidGVuYW50SWQiOiJ0XzU1Y2NkMjM4IiwiaWF0IjoxNzc2OTMzNjM0LCJleHAiOjE3NzY5MzQ1MzR9.eqA6Ba0Bo2MLe_wX06LcV77SQ37PLrY8pxdkVuBge1s38fxVLxjurxGSSo6RyMvB

### 로그인 - 잘못된 비밀번호
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"email":"test2@email.com","password":"wrong"}

### 로그인 - 없는 이메일
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"email":"noone@email.com","password":"1234"}

### 로그인
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"email":"test2@email.com","password":"1234"}

### 회원가입
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{"email":"test2@email.com","password":"1234","name":"test2"}

### 회원가입 - 중복 이메일 테스트
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{"email":"test2@email.com","password":"1234","name":"test2"}

### API Key 발급 (JWT 인증)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants/me/api-keys
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIzIiwidGVuYW50SWQiOiJ0XzU1Y2NkMjM4IiwiaWF0IjoxNzc2OTMzNjM0LCJleHAiOjE3NzY5MzQ1MzR9.eqA6Ba0Bo2MLe_wX06LcV77SQ37PLrY8pxdkVuBge1s38fxVLxjurxGSSo6RyMvB